description_html: The Katachi Collection is named for the Japanese concept that combines “kata,” meaning form, and “chi,” meaning magic. “Katachi is for lovers of craftsmanship. The meticulous construction yields graceful designs that are magical, ergonomic masterpieces," says Janice Feldman, JANUS et Cie founder and collection designer. Made from powder coated aluminum and hand woven JANUSfiber, Katachi features four new, variegated hues for an enchanting effect.
